name: Vegetarian Alien
description:
As a foodie alien you are looking forward to try new dishes from Earth. What better than some ecological veggies? For some reason a farmer is around the veggies you found and is trying to stop you picking them up...

Music used in Vegetarian Alien:

-  Fast Paced Electronic Loop by SintelV

- Folk Moon Loop by MuzaProduction

- Success Resolution Video Game Fanfare Sound Effect by FunWithSound

- Jingle Win 00 by LittleRobotSoundFactory
